Trade/Device Name(s): RNA Medical Glucose and β-Ketone Calibration Verification Controls
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Abbott Diabetes Care Precision Xceed Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Monitoring System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for RNA Medical Glucose and β-Ketone Calibration Verification Controls as assayed QC material to verify calibration and linearity of glucose and ketone testing on Abbott Precision Xceed Pro System.
Indications for Use Summary: For confirming calibration and linearity of glucose and β-ketone at upper, lower, and mid-range points using the Precision Xceed Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Monitoring System; intended for use by healthcare professionals.
